line_1: And at the amorous see-saw, won the match:
line_2: Thee, with her net, she found the means to catch,
The scholar bulfinch aims to catch

line_1: Where counsellors dispute, and cockers match,
line_2: And Caledonian earls in concert scratch;

line_1: Guide the nice conduct of a daring match,
line_2: And o'er th' equestrian rights, with care paternal watch.

line_1: To prove yourself the drunkard's match,
line_2: Have clapt and chorus'd ev'ry catch —
